{"tid":1360724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"727元朗遊行劇本","createTime":"2019-07-24T12:04:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T12:17:19.000Z","uid":53117,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b678ad8fb66532a7f0d59a5df7e5c82bd036c8f0","tid":1360724,"uid":53117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:04:08.000Z","msg":"我見到咁多post 討論應該和理非定去搞祠堂，然後互屌一毛，所以就大概預演下當日中共嘅劇本 <br />\n1. 遊行到咁上下有黑衫人去搞破壞燒祠堂 （可以係真黑衫or 假黑衫or mixed, not important）<br />\n2. 白衫'村民'出嚟同黑衫理論再起衝突，克警到場兩邊都拉<br />\n3. 散band後上連登互屌應唔應該攬黑衫燒祠堂<br />\n4. 之係係點自己諗<br />\n<br />\n小弟唔夠醒諗唔到咩好嘅解決方法，但每次都真係好擔心個運動會俾輿論搞散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家可唔可以集思廣益下點拆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"261a2b0a23320158ffc8d28d419f1694e1c64778","tid":1360724,"uid":53117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:05:05.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"795ffb4746fb38278e9a9ca10584020bbddb1958","tid":1360724,"uid":53117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:05:18.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e98c6377a4cb2515ba7877a89f495d97e4176edd","tid":1360724,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:06:28.000Z","msg":"[知己知彼]進入三毛思考領域，請連仔幫手<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1224185\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1224185</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n幫手推上熱門"},{"pid":"78cb2091fcec30911838c4d6501af23a5fe3cfcc","tid":1360724,"uid":259321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:08:07.000Z","msg":"唔好意思!!<br />\n後日0726就係機場集會!!!<br />\n機場有無數外國旅客!!!<br />\n係對外發出香港嘅SOS求救訊號嘅大好機會!!!<br />\n一定要搞大佢!!!<br />\n宜家一齊推&darr;&darr;&darr;<br />\n<br />\n❲0726機場❳ 多國語言 發動全球文宣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1360237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1360237</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[繼續開花] 到我地機師做野喇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1359574\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.k